{"tid":1448853,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實班狗夜晚點訓得著","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:19:13.000Z","uid":196978,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c718896f9adaaa5a0036779734d7e81c939f5581","tid":1448853,"uid":196978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"親手射爆人地隻眼<br />\n打到人牙都甩埋都仲要向傷口施壓<br />\n近距離數射一班年青人嘅血肉之軀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我從來都唔喊<br />\n但啲新聞 真係睇到我眼濕濕<br />\n<br />\n香港對我黎講一早死左<br />\n但到底 我要做啲乜嘢先可以幫助到佢地<br />\n保護到依班仲對香港有希望嘅年青人"},{"pid":"540c0b9990e3792300dc0984983fc2a1f0fb33dd","tid":1448853,"uid":74869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:11.000Z","msg":"請各位身邊人自行組隊 可信之人 5-8人為佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n進行袋袋平安計劃。兒女絕對係好事<br />\n<br />\n發夢係公廁 巴士 寫popo死全家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住我地呢一代都懷有仇恨種子 幾時爆無人知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實更加證明我地反對條例係岩 未同化大陸都咁樣<br />\n通過後想反抗未出門都拉左或被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ab6e90d755016a065960e089cacafd0263b0cd","tid":1448853,"uid":254869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"唔單只狗，係香港人都今晚都唔會瞓得著"},{"pid":"9ae5faf494d42c4c8681706589dd7960e98b1430","tid":1448853,"uid":196978,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"75ab6e90d755016a065960e089cacafd0263b0cd","tid":1448853,"uid":254869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"唔單只狗，係香港人都今晚都唔會瞓得著"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:22.000Z","msg":"都無諗住瞓<br />\n個社會已經去到一個病態嘅地步<br />\n我以為自己已經夠仆街<br />\n但原來人性可以咁醜陋"},{"pid":"37ad9b8d862fb4bc91f0c3c31a09fbcf700a335c","tid":1448853,"uid":179634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:28.000Z","msg":"而加個個星期日都訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /